import React from 'react'; import './ChatView.css'; const ChatView = ({ data, stats }) => { return (

Chat View

AI-powered data analysis and insights

Welcome to the AI Chat Assistant! I can help you analyze your engineering data.

Here's a summary of your current data:

  • Total Runs: {stats?.overall_stats?.total_runs || 0}
  • Passed Runs: {stats?.overall_stats?.passed_runs || 0}
  • Failed Runs: {stats?.overall_stats?.failed_runs || 0}
  • Success Rate: {stats?.overall_stats?.total_runs ? Math.round((stats.overall_stats.passed_runs / stats.overall_stats.total_runs) * 100) : 0}%

You can ask me questions about:

  • Performance trends
  • Stage analysis
  • Project insights
  • Data patterns
); }; export default ChatView;
